reviews.review_text: All mediocre electric sets on the weekend shows here, all of which I was at. The best acoustic set is definitely the 11th !

Are you kidding? This electric set smokes! High energy renditions of amost everything. Good vocals, and Jerry is on. This compares well to 1977 gigs.

The first set is also great. But listen to the soundboard version also available here.
goods Black Peter is Jerry's favorite.

Excellent show I think this show is very good. Of course, not the dead at their best but Music Never Stopped till the end of the show is superb. The acoustic set is nice too, definitely give it a listen!
